    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some fading on the roof's clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is intact but has some staining and minor wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will eventually need attention to the suspension and a minor oil leak. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a lower price point who doesn't mind some cosmetic and mechanical character.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
