      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative example of the E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This vehicle exhibits exceptional mechanical integrity, with the high-pressure Double-VANOS system and individual throttle bodies functioning in perfect synchronicity. Critical preventative maintenance, including the rod bearing service and rear subframe reinforcement, has been meticulously performed to ensure the chassis handles high lateral loads without compromise. The factory-spec limited-slip differential and unmodified suspension geometry provide the precise, communicative feedback enthusiasts demand. Preserved in concours-level condition, this M3 retains its original factory-honed dynamics and aesthetic purity, making it a definitive collector-grade specimen.",
